%U A395261 273577034,584692360,1239460350,2607259832,5444266882,11288922942,23251902844,47586826524,96795128832
%N A395261 Self-convolution of A000293.
%C A395261 Conjecturally, log(a(n)) ~ 2^(1/4) * C_3 * n^(3/4) as n -> infinity, where C_3 = 1.822... is the asymptotic constant for solid partitions (i.e., log(A000293(n)) ~ C_3 * n^(3/4)).
%H A395261 Thomas DiFiore, <a href="/A395261/b395261.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..50</a>
%H A395261 Nicolas Destainville and Suresh Govindarajan, <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/1406.5605">Estimating the asymptotics of solid partitions</a>, arXiv:1406.5605 [cond-mat.stat-mech], 2014; J. Stat. Phys. 158 (2015) 950-967.
%F A395261 a(n) = Sum_{k=0..n} A000293(k) * A000293(n-k).
%e A395261 a(3) = A000293(0)*A000293(3) + A000293(1)*A000293(2) + A000293(2)*A000293(1) + A000293(3)*A000293(0) = 1*10 + 1*4 + 4*1 + 10*1 = 28.
%Y A395261 Cf. A000293.
